      <title>独家：日本九州电力将等待美国查尔斯湖液化天然气政策的明确</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/japans-kyushu-electric-wait-us-lng-policy-clarity-lake-charles-2024-02-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本九州电力公司一位高管表示，将等到美国恢复向新的液化天然气（LNG）项目发放出口许可证后，再决定是否投资查尔斯湖项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/japans-kyushu-electric-wait-us-lng-policy-clarity-lake-charles-2024-02-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 09:31:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡航空第三季度利润因强劲的旅行需求而增长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/singapore-airlines-posts-5-rise-q3-profit-2024-02-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡航空 (SIA) 周二公布，受主要市场强劲的航空旅行需求推动，其季度净利润增长 4.9%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/singapore-airlines-posts-5-rise-q3-profit-2024-02-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 09:29:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼大选落败候选人呼吁议会调查</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/defeated-indonesian-election-candidates-call-parliamentary-probe-2024-02-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周印度尼西亚总统选举中落选的两名候选人敦促议会调查有关选举前夕违规行为的投诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/defeated-indonesian-election-candidates-call-parliamentary-probe-2024-02-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 09:22:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>律师称韩国强迫劳动受害者从日本公司获得“赔偿”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/skorea-forced-labour-victim-receives-compensation-japanese-firm-family-lawyer-2024-02-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名在 1910 年至 1945 年日本占领期间被迫为一家日本公司工作的韩国男子的家人从他工作的日本公司收到了钱，这是强迫劳动受害者首次在法律案件中获得此类资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/skorea-forced-labour-victim-receives-compensation-japanese-firm-family-lawyer-2024-02-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 07:57:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西航空工业公司高管表示，受普拉特发动机问题的影响较小，但也不能幸免</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/embraer-less-affected-by-pratt-engine-issues-not-immune-executive-says-2024-02-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[与其他一些公司相比，巴西航空工业公司受普惠公司问题的影响较小。巴西飞机制造商的一位高管周二表示，惠特尼发动机也未能幸免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/embraer-less-affected-by-pratt-engine-issues-not-immune-executive-says-2024-02-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 07:53:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>海外旅游回暖，中国游客涌向东南亚</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-tourists-flock-southeast-asia-overseas-travel-bounces-back-2024-02-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[农历新年期间，中国游客涌向亚洲各地的旅游热点，新加坡、泰国和马来西亚等目的地的游客人数和消费都超过了新冠疫情前的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-tourists-flock-southeast-asia-overseas-travel-bounces-back-2024-02-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 07:11:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高监管机构要求中国金融部门遵循共产党的价值观</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/top-watchdogs-tell-chinas-finance-sector-follow-communist-party-values-2024-02-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中共官方报纸周二称，中国最高金融监管机构誓言要继续开展行动，确保该行业遵守共产党的价值观并为经济服务，同时避免“过度”和“鲁莽”的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/top-watchdogs-tell-chinas-finance-sector-follow-communist-party-values-2024-02-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 06:36:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾与美国联合空中巡逻“保护领土”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-joint-air-patrol-with-us-protect-territory-2024-02-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在北京指责马尼拉挑起事端后，一名菲律宾军方官员周二表示，菲律宾与美国进行联合空中巡逻的目的是保护南海的领土和国家利益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-joint-air-patrol-with-us-protect-territory-2024-02-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 06:20:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国希望货币改革将大部分 NDF 交易转向现货交付</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/south-korea-talks-with-euroclear-boost-won-accessibility-fx-official-says-2024-02-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级政府官员周二表示，韩国希望其货币交易改革的努力将把很大一部分交易量从无本金交割远期市场转移到即期货币市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/south-korea-talks-with-euroclear-boost-won-accessibility-fx-official-says-2024-02-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 06:02:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚竞争监管机构警告 ANZ、Suncorp 收购案不予批准</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/australias-competition-regulator-says-proposed-anz-suncorp-merger-shows-need-2024-02-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[反垄断监管机构负责人告诉路透社，澳大利亚竞争法庭周二批准了澳新银行以 42 亿澳元（32 亿美元）收购 Suncorp 银行资产的提议，但这并不意味着类似的交易将被放弃。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/australias-competition-regulator-says-proposed-anz-suncorp-merger-shows-need-2024-02-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 05:58:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
